**PROJECT ON GROCERY SALES ANALYSIS USING MICROSOFT POWER BI**

**Introduction**
Power BI is a cloud-based and on-premises business intelligence tool developed by Microsoft to analyze and visualize data from multiple sources. This project aims to use Power BI for analyzing grocery sales data, helping businesses track total revenue, sales trends, and customer preferences.
Power BI enables self-service business intelligence, allowing users to create interactive reports and dashboards without needing advanced technical expertise.
